      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nThis patch includes Cheng's suggested change.  Note this is exactly the logic used in 2.3 for MDS_OPEN_BY_FID, so it should be sound.\n\nOne question:\nmti_cross_ref is not checked when MDS_OPEN_BY_FID is set.  (This is true for 2.3 as well.)\n\nIs this correct?",
