      "date": "2013-10-10 03:34:45.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nopen by fid won't cross mdt because client will talk to the mdt where the fid exists directly, in current code if the file with the specified name is on another mdt, mdt will notify client with -EREMOTE, and client will open again on that mdt(this is done in lmv). And after the change of lu-3765 on master code, since open request won't pack name any more, client will only talk to the mdt where the fid exists.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
