      },
      "date": "2013-10-23 15:13:37.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nnew versions must take care about interop issues by themselves not requiring old versions to be \"fixed\". in other words, this is LU-3544 which must be fixed. AFAICS in the jira ticket, LU-3544 was already reverted and planned to be fixed for 2.4/2.5 versions. do I understand correctly the current patch is not planned for landing to 2.1 anymore ? it seems the jira ticket says it, so just to confirm...",
