        },
        "subject": "LU-3765 fid: add OPEN_BY_FID for forward compatibility",
        "message": "LU-3765 fid: add OPEN_BY_FID for forward compatibility\n\nNow that 2.5 will enable open by fid by default, to support\n2.5 client <-> 2.1 server interop, add OPEN_BY_FID for 2.1\nserver.\n\nSet DISP_IT_EXECD for open_anon_by_fid() in case 2.5 client\nwill assert on this.\n\nSigned-off-by: Lai Siyao <lai.siyao@intel.com>\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrel <paf@cray.com>\nChange-Id: I616e0099b2165c3abbc8ccf8d86da8fcc04ab88c\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_1"
    }
  },
